name: No. 3, 2017

description:
Grant Morrison's epic creation continues.

The conclusion to the grand hunt! Abhimanyu and his cousin Gatok must hide in the dense jungles from Emperor Duryodhana's unstoppable assassins: the insidious Ashwatthama, and the deadly Durma! Hope is running out as the inexperienced duo find themselves prey to the deadliest predators in the history of the world!
